		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">History of China</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">"Imperial China" redirects here. For a history book by that name, see <a href="/wiki/Imperial_China:_900%E2%80%931800" title="Imperial China: 900–1800">Imperial China: 900–1800</a>.</div>
<div class="metadata plainlinks topicon" id="protected-icon" style="position:absolute; z-index:100; right:55px; top:10px;">
<div><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Protection_policy#semi" title="This article is semi-protected."><img alt="Semi-protected" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Padlock-silver-medium.svg/20px-Padlock-silver-medium.svg.png" width="20" height="20" border="0" /></a></div>
</div>
<div class="dablink">This article is about the history of China prior to October 1, 1949.  For the history of modern mainland China, see <a href="/wiki/History_of_the_People%27s_Republic_of_China" title="History of the People's Republic of China">History of the People's Republic of China</a>. For the history of modern Taiwan, see <a href="/wiki/History_of_the_Republic_of_China" title="History of the Republic of China">History of the Republic of China</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Territories_of_Dynasties_in_China.gif" class="image" title="Territories occupied by different dynasties as well as modern political states throughout the history of China."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/54/Territories_of_Dynasties_in_China.gif" width="250" height="241" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Territories_of_Dynasties_in_China.gif" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Territories occupied by different dynasties as well as modern political states throughout the history of China.</div>
</div>
