<li>Pelliot, Paul. 1904. "Deux itinéraires de Chine en Inde à la fin du VIII<sup>e</sup> siècle." <i>BEFEO</i> 4 (1904), pp. 131–413.</li>
<li>Schafer, Edward H. 1963. <i>The Golden Peaches of Samarkand: A study of T’ang Exotics</i>. University of California Press. Berkeley and Los Angeles. 1st paperback edition. 1985. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0520054628" class="internal">ISBN 0-520-05462-8</a>.</li>
<li>Schafer, Edward H. 1967. <i>The Vermilion Bird: T’ang Images of the South</i>. University of California Press, Berkeley and Los Angeles. Reprint 1985. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0520054628" class="internal">ISBN 0-520-05462-8</a>.</li>
