<li><a href="/wiki/Herbert_Feis" title="Herbert Feis">Feis, Herbert</a>, <i>The China Tangle: The American Effort in China from Pearl Harbor to the Marshall Mission</i>, Princeton University Press, 1953.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Ken_Hammond" title="Ken Hammond">Hammond, Kenneth J.</a> <a href="http://www.thegreatcourses.com/ttcx/coursedesclong2.aspx?cid=8320&amp;id=8320&amp;d=From+Yao+to+Mao%3A+5000+Years+of+Chinese+History&amp;pc=History%20-%20Ancient%20and%20Medieval" class="external text" title="http://www.thegreatcourses.com/ttcx/coursedesclong2.aspx?cid=8320&amp;id=8320&amp;d=From+Yao+to+Mao%3A+5000+Years+of+Chinese+History&amp;pc=History%20-%20Ancient%20and%20Medieval" rel="nofollow">From Yao to Mao: 5000 Years of Chinese History</a>. The Teaching Company, 2004. (A lecture on DVD.)</li>
